      *    * Subroutine di costruzione del box                         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-dti-ods-box-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Box                                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "BX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lto                  .
