      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-acc-pds-aev        =    zero
                     go to acc-num-prt-300.
           move      w-acc-pds-aev-saa    to   w-acc-num-prt-saa      .
           move      w-acc-cod-dpz        to   w-acc-num-prt-dpz      .
           move      w-acc-pds-aev-prg    to   w-acc-num-prt-prg      .
       acc-num-prt-300.
