      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-num-prt-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-num-prt-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-num-prt-999.
