      *                  * Riciclo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-pag-sdc-100.
       vis-pag-sdc-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione riga piena                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Descrizione                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           add       7
                     w-sdc-wrk-c01      giving v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-bro-des-rig
                    (w-sdc-wrk-rig)       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
