      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-bro-tip-rig
                    (w-sdc-wrk-rig)       not  = "C" and
                     w-bro-tip-rig
                    (w-sdc-wrk-rig)       not  = "A"
                     go to vis-pag-sdc-320.
